  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HttpExecutorService
    A Service which is responsible of execution an HttpRequest
    HttpResponse
    Wraps a Response from the Jersey Client
    ListType
    Decorator interface to designate List Type results and to insure that an EmptyList is returned in 404/NotFound responses
    PropagateResponse
    Allows for propagation depending on the state of a response.
